Swansea have revived talks and agreed a fee with Marseille for Dimitri Payet.

Marseille are happy to sell for £6.5million but the 27-year-old winger is unsure about the move.

The Welsh club are also interested in West Ham target Timothee Kolodziejczak, the Nice left-back.

