Targeted: And Crystal Palace are chasing Jonjo Shelvey

Meanwhile, Crystal Palace maintain an interest in Swansea midfielder Jonjo Shelvey.

The 22-year-old made 32 appearances in the Premier League last season, scoring six goals.

The Eagles are hoping to strengthen their midfield option with Jose Campana finalising his move to Sampdoria.

